---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import Breadcrumbs from "../components/shared/Breadcrumbs.astro";
import { getBreadcrumbSchema, SITE_URL } from "../helpers/schema";
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, "");

const jsonLd = [
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "WebPage",
    url: `${SITE_URL}/terms/`,
    name: "Terms and Conditions",
    description: "Terms and Conditions for BestPropFirms.com — rules governing the use of our site and services.",
    isPartOf: { "@id": `${SITE_URL}/#website` },
  },
  getBreadcrumbSchema([
    { name: "Home", url: "/" },
    { name: "Terms and Conditions" },
  ]),
];
---

<Base
  title="Terms and Conditions | BestPropFirms.com"
  description="Terms and Conditions for BestPropFirms.com — rules governing the use of our site and services."
  jsonLd={jsonLd}
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-[#0d1b2a] text-white py-16 px-4">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-teal-400 mb-2">Legal</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-black mb-4">Terms and Conditions</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-300 text-lg max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
        The rules and conditions governing your use of BestPropFirms.com.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pt-4">
    <Breadcrumbs crumbs={[{ name: "Home", url: "/" }, { name: "Terms and Conditions" }]} />
  </div>

  <!-- Content -->
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-10 shadow-sm prose-container">

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Background</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        The BestPropFirms.com website is run by Compare Prop Firms Pty Ltd of Jacovides Tower 1st Floor, 81-83 Grivas Digenis Avenue, Nicosia, 1090, Cyprus (BestPropFirms).
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        BestPropFirms is authorised under Corporate Authorised Representative of GUILDFORDS FUNDS MANAGEMENT PTY LTD (ACN 602 779 993) in accordance with AFSL No. 471379 (A/R No. 001274082).
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Our objective is to simplify the evaluation and selection of prop trading companies (the Service) for beginners and experienced users (such as you). BestPropFirms also includes other seasonal products and services that may be introduced occasionally.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Regardless of the platform used to access this website (Site), whether on a computer, phone, tablet or any other device (Device), the user agrees to the Terms and Conditions set by BestPropFirms. The user also consents to the Privacy Policy, disclaimers, and notices placed by BestPropFirms (Terms and Conditions).
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        The use of this Site, through browsing articles and utilising comparison tables, entails the user's acknowledgment of BestPropFirms's Terms and Conditions (as updated periodically).
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-slate-200">Description of Site and Service</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">The user can access the Service on our Site, which comprises of:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8 space-y-1">
        <li>Reviews of prop trading companies</li>
        <li>Prop firm trading guides</li>
        <li>Comparison tables on different prop firms that you examine on the Site</li>
        <li>Several communication outlets such as live chat, phone, and email for sharing trade data</li>
        <li>Any additional features such as products and services (Add-On Services) offered by BestPropFirms that are relevant to the Service – may include products and services from third parties</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-slate-200">Website</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        The Site aims to provide users with data on Prop trading companies or prop trading firms (collectively, Prop Firms) to help you get familiarised with each prop firm's features. In doing so, we aspire to direct you toward the appropriate prop firm for your needs.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-slate-200">Privacy</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        We value every user's privacy. Please review our <a href={`${base}/privacy`} class="text-teal-600 hover:text-teal-700 underline">Privacy Policy</a> on how the Site collects and manages any personal information you provide.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-slate-200">Your Use of the Site</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Our Site offers Services free of charge. With that goal in mind, BestPropFirms discloses the contractual relationships with the Prop Firms reviewed on the Site. We may receive payments from them through our affiliate links present in our reviews.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">Furthermore, BestPropFirms acknowledges that:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8 space-y-1">
        <li>There may be information present on the Site provided by Prop Firms that is yet to be verified by BestPropFirms</li>
        <li>BestPropFirms manually obtains information through constant research and does not receive data automatically from any prop firm</li>
        <li>Data presented aim to compare each prop firm objectively, however, there are instances where they can be interpreted subjectively</li>
        <li>Any statement we present on the Site is purely educational and by no means to be considered a governmental policy, law statement, or regulation</li>
        <li>Regarding Australian prop firms, AUD (Australian dollars) is used as the display price on fees and spreads</li>
        <li>BestPropFirms is not a registered ASIC provider</li>
        <li>Every comparison and information we present on the Site are overviews only</li>
        <li>BestPropFirms promptly addresses and corrects any inaccuracy when such is brought to our attention</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-slate-200">Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Trading forex online by partnering with a prop firm comes with risks and may lead to a financial loss.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Examine the prop firm's disclosure statements before going with a prop firm and/or doing any transaction. Conduct your enquiry on the eligibility of their products or services, and if necessary, seek professional advice. Moreover, if you have any concerns with regard to the products and services of a prop firm, contact your professional service provider.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">To the maximum extent permitted by law:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4 space-y-1">
        <li>We disclaim all guarantees about the accuracy, completeness, correctness, reliability, promptness or suitability of any content or information on the Sites or the Service</li>
        <li>We cannot guarantee the prop firm information's accuracy, promptness or totality, nor the quality of the outcomes acquired from the Site</li>
        <li>We cannot certify the Site's or supporting servers' components to be free from viruses, defects, or other harmful elements, nor that they will run devoid of errors or disruptions</li>
        <li>We (staff, executives, agents, or representatives) will not be accountable for any direct or indirect damage or loss to any individual or entity, regardless of the cause (due to negligence or others), that has occurred from your interaction or inability to use the Service or Site, or by relying on the content we provide on the Site</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">You agree to indemnify us from any claim, damage, allegation, repercussions, losses, or costs (including but not limited to attorney fees) encountered or experienced by us, directly or indirectly, in relation to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4 space-y-1">
        <li>Your non-compliance with the Terms and Conditions</li>
        <li>Any inaccuracy or breach in your guarantees or statements</li>
        <li>Your activities on the Site</li>
        <li>Your usage of the Service</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        The Terms and Conditions are not meant to be interpreted or enforced in a way that alters, limits, or affects any condition, guarantee, right, or remedy that the law legally mandates, and that cannot be legally dismissed, modified, or restricted.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-slate-200">Access</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        We provide you with a non-exclusive, non-assignable, revocable, non-sub-licensable licence and the right to access the Site on any platform and utilise the Service in strict accordance with the Terms and Conditions. Any engagement or usage of the Site or the Service in opposition of the Terms and Conditions is prohibited.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        We have the authority to temporarily or permanently restrict access to the Site or Service at any given time for any reason – this includes but is not limited to update or maintenance of the Site. We will not be held liable to you or any other person for revoked or interrupted access to the Site.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-slate-200">Customer Data</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        While engaging with the Service, you may decide to share, upload, convey, or allow BestPropFirms to access your data, information, software or content (Customer Data). You consent to our and our third-party providers' use, access, modification, copy, and storage of your Customer Data to deliver the Service to you, having no limit to disseminate said data to our third-party providers as well as to gather and employ data as defined in our Privacy Policy and any other portion of these conditions.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-slate-200">Eligibility</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">Eligibility to access the Site and Service entails the following requirements that you state to be correct that you:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8 space-y-1">
        <li>Are of legal age (18) or older</li>
        <li>Are not presently banned from using the Service</li>
        <li>Are not a business competitor, nor utilising the Service for purposes of competing with our company</li>
        <li>Will not infringe on our or any individual's rights (including intellectual property rights)</li>
        <li>Are fully authorised to agree to any contractual understanding with us regarding the usage of the Site or Service, which includes agreeing to the Terms and Conditions while not violating any contract you may have with any other party</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-slate-200">Consent and Conduct</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Please closely examine the Terms and Conditions before engaging with the Site. By accessing or navigating through the Site on any device, you confirm that you have read, comprehended and agreed to the Terms and Conditions in its totality, together with any other law or regulation applicable. If you disagree with any of the set Terms and Conditions, please do not use the Site.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        Upon accessing, browsing, and using the Site or Service, you must observe all the laws, regulations, and codes and perform by following commonly acknowledged industry standards and practices.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-slate-200">Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-3">
        Content featured on the Site, including but not limited to text, graphics, images, photographs, illustrations, designs, music, audio, software, data collections and all intellectual property rights incorporated (our content), are owned by us, our partners, affiliates, licensors or content provider. You recognise and consent that:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8 space-y-1">
        <li>Our content is and always be our exclusive property, with corresponding content belonging to our partners, affiliates, licensors or content provider</li>
        <li>You are allowed to access our content on the Site following the Terms and Conditions and any pertinent legislation governing intellectual property, including but not limited to the Copyright Act 1968 (Cth)</li>
        <li>You use our content for strictly educational, personal, and non-commercial intents only, and that said usage does not grant you rights regarding copyright, trademarks, designs, or other intellectual property relevant to the Site's content</li>
        <li>You will not copy, alter, reproduce, spread, transfer, publish, license, produce derivative creations from, reuse, or sell any element of the Site or our content without our written permission</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-slate-200">Third Party Sites</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        The Site may include links to different websites, products, applications or services under third parties (Third Party Sites). We do not promote, observe, control, and have no responsibility for the content and policies on any Third Party Sites. We also do not warrant nor represent any accuracy, quality or legitimacy of the content on any Third Party Sites. You can access any Third Party Sites through the Site at your own risk. We highly recommend investigating before depending on any content on any Third Party Sites.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-slate-200">Updates</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        We uphold the right to update or make changes to the Terms and Conditions at any given time without notifying you, in effect upon its publication to the Site. By resuming your use and access to the Site after any changes to the Terms and Conditions, you acknowledge that you have read and comprehended the new Terms and Conditions.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-slate-200">Complaints</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        If you know of or suspect any infringements of these Terms and Conditions, don't hesitate to get in touch with us right away via email.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-slate-200">Applicable Law</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        The Terms and Conditions are ruled by and construed under the laws of Victoria, Australia. By accessing and engaging with the Site on any device, you commit to Victoria's courts' sole jurisdiction and waive any objections to the jurisdiction or medium in such courts.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-slate-200">Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
        Should you have any question, reaction, comment, or concern about the Terms and Conditions, don't hesitate to reach out via email at <strong>justin[at]compareforexbrokers.com</strong>.
      </p>

    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
